title: Grammy Nominees From Warner-Reprise 1994 (Big Papi)
description:
---------------------------------------------------------------------
Grammy Nominees From Warner-Reprise 1994 (Big Papi) Industry 2-CD Set

---------------------------------------------------------------------

This is a 2-CD white labelled set that Warner Records used to submit its Grammy nominees for the year 1994. All meta data was not in the online database so Big Papi had to handcut some MP3 tags. Please excuse any errors. The compilation also lacked AccurateRip hash comparisons and the CD's were not in the best of shape. They required lots of cleaning and buffing. Spot check was done and the songs sound good.

Treat this more of a music history release for 1994. These are not the top songs of 1994 but the top songs for each category as submitted by one record label. Big Papi has no idea what songs won that year. These are submissions only. Read the cover art to see which Grammy categories each song fits into.

Thanks and welcome to 1994! Where were you? Big Papi likes that Feed The Tree song :)

- Big Papi
